To get in contact with the partnership team at George Brown College, please fill out the form or sign up using the "Sign Up Now" button. You can also reach out to ask.george@georgebrown.ca for inquiries. The college's phone number is 416-415-2000 and TTY number is 1-877-515-5559. The college has a social media hub that can be visited. Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, and tours may be kept up to date by signing up. Please note that the information contained in the website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered as a representation, offer or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
